Package microgram.api

Class Post

  • java.lang.Object
    • microgram.api.Post
  • public class Post
extends Object
    Represents a Post. A post has an unique postId, and a single ownerId profile; comprises of an image, taken at some location and stored at some mediaurl; is timestamped and has a number of likes.

    smd
